entries.journal_entry_description: Qakkee believes he's the greatest hunter in the galaxy. Prove that you are his equal!
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Hunt down 12 Snorbals on Lok and bring their trunks back to Qakkee.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Qakkee with the Snorbal trunks, before they start to smell.
